{"tid":1716322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[裝修]有間国企押運公司會係中共春袋！","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T07:16:58.000Z","uid":60260,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"19627195b6d33687756ef54c89b13bec6f0da7a0","tid":1716322,"uid":60260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友係呢間中資押運公司員工<br />\n佢同我講雖然公司入面同事大部分後生而且極黃<br />\n但始終係大陸開落黎插旗既<br />\n<br />\n而佢哋由於唔夠車用,所以每日都會有4-5架大陸公司左軚裝甲車由深圳過香港開工,宜家咁既局面就一定唔會查佢地車<br />\n<br />\n所以入面會唔會運咩裝備軍火落黎屈手足真係無人會知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而最春袋既係:佢哋每日都會由香港運過百億人仔上去央行,所以一定唔可以令佢地無錢運到上去製造骨牌效應呀!!</span>"},{"pid":"fca49a41e3406f829cfdd8ba75d9815f4aef779d","tid":1716322,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:17:43.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"eabf7b2671983b124157acbf8a1f04dcd3d64429","tid":1716322,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=7ba2ecad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F119434944634944307